addDefaultSearches

public void addDefaultSearches()
Populates the SearchControl with a default set of Search objects. This will add:
  1. WebSearch
  2. LocalSearch
  3. VideoSearch
  4. BlogSearch
  5. NewsSearch
  6. BookSearch
  7. ImageSearch
